Preheat oven to 350Â°F.

Cream @butter{1%cup} and @sugar{1.5%cup} together until light and fluffy.

Add @eggs{2} and @vanilla{1%tsp} to the creamed mixture and beat well.

Mix in @flour{2%cup} and @baking-powder{2%tsp} until just combined.

Pour into a greased pan and bake for 30-35 minutes until golden brown and a toothpick inserted in the center comes out clean.
